.TH "nfp_port_configure" 9 "nfp_port_configure" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nfp_port_configure \- helper to set the interface configured bit
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" nfp_port_configure
.BI "(struct net_device *netdev "  ","
.BI "bool configed "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "netdev" 12
net_device instance
.IP "configed" 12
Desired state
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Helper to set the ifup/ifdown state on the PHY only if there is a physical
interface associated with the netdev.
.SH "RETURN"
0 - configuration successful (or no change);
-ERRNO - configuration failed.
